# Deny by default: only the server build graph enters the BuildKit context.
**

!Dockerfile
!.dockerignore
!Cargo.toml
!Cargo.lock
!LICENSE

# Cargo.lock describes every workspace member. Their manifests and sources are
# needed for a locked workspace load; cargo still compiles only spurfire-server.
!crates/
!crates/**

# Workspace patch paths are included because Cargo validates them while loading
# the root manifest, even though spurfire-server does not compile game networking.
!vendor/
!vendor/boringtun/
!vendor/boringtun/**

# Never re-include local credentials if one appears below an allowed tree.
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.key
**/*.p12
**/*.pem
